---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Resume | Remoun Metyas" description="Product engineer with 15 years of experience building systems where the stakes are real.">
  <div class="resume">
    <header>
      <h1>Remoun Metyas</h1>
      <p class="resume-contact">
        Bay Area, CA · 
        <a href="mailto:work@remoun.me">work@remoun.me</a> · 
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/remoun">LinkedIn</a>
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="resume-section">
      <h2>Summary</h2>
      <p>
        Product engineer with 15 years of experience building systems where the stakes are real — fraud prevention, financial inclusion, safety-critical infrastructure.
      </p>
      <p>
        The through-line: what does it take to make connection possible at scale?
      </p>
      <p>
        Strong foundation in platform engineering and systems design, with a bias toward the product surface where infrastructure meets the people it serves.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="resume-section">
      <h2>Skills</h2>
      <p>
        Full-stack development and technical leadership across web, mobile, and backend systems.<br>
        Technologies include Go, Python, Rust, Kotlin, Java, C++, TypeScript, React, SQL, gRPC, PostgreSQL, Kafka.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="resume-section">
      <h2>Key Accomplishments</h2>

      <div class="resume-entry">
        <p class="resume-entry__title">Expanding Access to Microfinance</p>
        <p>Co-owned the launch of Kiva's Auto-Lending engine and the $5 Notes migration, which lowered the minimum loan from $25 to $5 — making microfinance accessible to more first-time lenders and expanding Kiva's reach globally.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="resume-entry">
        <p class="resume-entry__title">Unifying Safety Tooling at Waymo</p>
        <p>Designed and built a generic event triage tool processing millions of driving events per week, replacing 4 bespoke tools and giving engineers a single interface to measure and improve Self-Driving System performance.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="resume-entry">
        <p class="resume-entry__title">Backend Platform for a Privacy-First Mobile Wallet</p>
        <p>Led backend services for Moby, Sentz's flagship wallet app — everything beyond the core blockchain. Took one service from PoC to production with CI, rate limiting, observability, and partner integrations.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="resume-entry">
        <p class="resume-entry__title">Scaling Traffic Enforcement Infrastructure</p>
        <p>Designed and shipped an event pipeline orchestrator for HaydenAI, consolidating fragmented dispatching into a robust, observable system. Led a multi-engineer effort to decouple fleets from violation processors, expanding operational flexibility and helping land a new client.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="resume-section">
      <h2>Experience</h2>
      <div class="experience-list">
        <div class="resume-entry">
          <div class="resume-entry__header">
            <span class="resume-entry__title">Senior Software Engineer · HaydenAI</span>
            <span class="resume-entry__date">Dec 2024 – Present</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resume-entry">
          <div class="resume-entry__header">
            <span class="resume-entry__title">Founder · RM Tech Consulting</span>
            <span class="resume-entry__date">Nov 2023 – Dec 2024</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resume-entry">
          <div class="resume-entry__header">
            <span class="resume-entry__title">Staff Software Engineer · Sentz <span class="fka">(fka MobileCoin)</span></span>
            <span class="resume-entry__date">Jan 2022 – Oct 2023</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resume-entry">
          <div class="resume-entry__header">
            <span class="resume-entry__title">Senior Software Engineer · Kiva</span>
            <span class="resume-entry__date">Jan 2020 – Nov 2021</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resume-entry">
          <div class="resume-entry__header">
            <span class="resume-entry__title">Software Engineer · Waymo</span>
            <span class="resume-entry__date">Mar 2016 – Jun 2019</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resume-entry">
          <div class="resume-entry__header">
            <span class="resume-entry__title">Software Engineer · Google</span>
            <span class="resume-entry__date">Nov 2011 – Mar 2016</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resume-entry">
          <div class="resume-entry__header">
            <span class="resume-entry__title">Co-Founder & CTO · Databracket</span>
            <span class="resume-entry__date">Jul 2010 – May 2012</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resume-entry">
          <div class="resume-entry__header">
            <span class="resume-entry__title">Software Engineer · Acuant Compliance <span class="fka">(fka IdentityMind)</span></span>
            <span class="resume-entry__date">Nov 2009 – Apr 2010</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resume-entry resume-entry--minor">
          <div class="resume-entry__header">
            <span class="resume-entry__title">Software Engineering Intern · Google (Gmail)</span>
            <span class="resume-entry__date">Jun 2008 – Aug 2008</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resume-entry resume-entry--minor">
          <div class="resume-entry__header">
            <span class="resume-entry__title">IT Intern · Egypt Post</span>
            <span class="resume-entry__date">Jun 2007 – Aug 2007</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resume-entry resume-entry--minor">
          <div class="resume-entry__header">
            <span class="resume-entry__title">Undergraduate TA · American University in Cairo</span>
            <span class="resume-entry__date">Feb 2007 – Jun 2007</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resume-entry resume-entry--minor">
          <div class="resume-entry__header">
            <span class="resume-entry__title">Database Administrator · Niceco Elevators</span>
            <span class="resume-entry__date">Sep 2003 – Jun 2005</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="resume-section">
      <h2>Education</h2>
      <div class="resume-entry">
        <div class="resume-entry__header">
          <span class="resume-entry__title">B.Sc. Computer Science</span>
          <span class="resume-entry__date">2009</span>
        </div>
        <p class="resume-entry__subtitle">American University in Cairo · Minors: Mathematics, Theatre</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="resume-section">
      <h2>Awards & Recognition</h2>
      <ul class="awards-list">
        <li>ACM ICPC World Finalist, 2008</li>
        <li>Google Search Citizenship Award, 2013</li>
        <li>Co-inventor, US Patent US20240420126A1: "System and Method for Providing Secure Transaction Data Access to Trusted Third Parties"</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .resume-contact {
    font-size: var(--size-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .resume-contact a {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .resume-contact a:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .resume-entry ul {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  .resume-entry li {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .resume-actions {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .resume-download {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--size-sm);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .fka {
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .experience-list .resume-entry {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .resume-entry--minor {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .resume-entry--minor .resume-entry__title {
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .awards-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .awards-list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .awards-list li::before {
    content: "·";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
</style>
